WEBVTT

00:01:28.617 --> 00:01:31.786
But I'm convinced that the answer
to the first one is no.

00:01:31.810 --> 00:01:33.333
When it comes to your career,

00:01:33.357 --> 00:01:36.762
"follow your passion"
can be a recipe for misery.

00:01:36.786 --> 00:01:40.420
Barack Obama: I want you to have passion,
but you have to have a strategy.

00:01:40.444 --> 00:01:46.978
(Theme music)

00:01:47.002 --> 00:01:50.684
AG: I'm Adam Grant, and this is WorkLife,
my podcast with TED.

00:01:50.708 --> 00:01:52.819
I'm an organizational psychologist.

00:01:52.843 --> 00:01:55.110
I study how to make work not suck.

00:01:55.743 --> 00:01:56.917
In this show,

00:01:56.941 --> 00:02:00.584
I'm inviting myself inside the minds
of some truly unusual people,